column30: With regard to HIV-positive individuals transmitting HIV through sexual contact, how accurate do you believe the slogan "Undetectable = Untransmittable" is?
column31: If a person living with HIV who maintains an Undetectable viral load by regularly taking effective medication, how much protection would this provide against HIV transmission?

column33: When did you most recently complete a HIV test?
column34: How many people do you know who regularly get tested for HIV?
column35:
People Living with HIV who maintain an Undetectable viral load by regularly taking effective medication cannot pass on HIV to their sexual partners. 
Did you know this prior to taking part in this survey?
